HB 387 Original 2026 Regular Session Gadberry
Abstract: Provides requirements for architects performing incidental engineering work.
Present law provides an exception to the rule that engineering work shall be supervised by
a licensed engineer, allowing architects to conduct certain engineering work incidental to
their architectural work on a given construction or renovation project.
